Description :
        From Tokyopop: Before Ekichi Onizuka would become "Great Teacher Onizuka". He and Ryuji Danma were the leaders of the famous biker gang, Oni Baku. When they weren't out riding around and getting into trouble, this duo could be found in school. Doing what you ask? Picking up young women of course!
